o thoroughly explore her robust influence on American popular culture.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aMotion picture actors and actressesxBiographyxUnited States. 0aMotion picture actors and actresseszUnited StatesvBiography. 0aSingersxBiographyxUnited States. 0aSingerszUnited StatesvBiography. 0aWomen singerszUnited StatesvBiography. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / Film & Video / General.2bisacsh  aamerican culture.  aamerican musicals.  aamerican theatre.  aannie get your gun.  abiographical.  abiography.  abroadway actress.  abroadway diva.  abroadway musical.  abroadway.  adancer.  adiva.  afamous actress.  agershwin brothers.  agolden age.  ahollywood.  alife story.  amusical theatre.  apopular culture.  ascrapbook.  asinger.  astage actors.  astage actress.  atheatre history.  atheatre.  atrue story.  auntold story.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013z978311069042240uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/978052092725440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520927254423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520927254/original  a978-3-11-069042-2  University of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles